  "description": "This is our simplified variation of a famous Uzbek rice dish plov (or pilaf). It may not be very authentic and uses the wrong meat (pork instead of lamb) but it’s still full of flavor that will make you smile and want to eat more. And you could make enough for all your friends or eat it yourself for several days.",
